r dimensional\nconfiguration spaces. Physical experiments using the proposed framework are\nfurther demonstrated on a humanoid robot that walks in several cluttered\nenvironments with narrow passages.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 10 Apr 2021 01:07:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 30 Jun 2022 03:25:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-26"}
