uced gaseous\nmethane. A finite difference scheme is used for the numerical integration.\nModel consistency is showed through numerical simulations which investigate the\neffect of the variation of some operating parameters on process performance.\nThe model is then applied to a real case scenario of engineering interest.\nSimulations produce results in good agreement with experimental observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 10 Apr 2021 14:22:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-10"}
