cent deep learning-based techniques showed significantly improved\nresults when tested with the proposed approach and achieved an average\ndetection accuracy of 97.47%, precision of 0.976 and F1 score of 0.979.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 10 Apr 2021 15:56:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 1 Mar 2022 16:30:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-31"}
